<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,1770,1976]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Remarks.—The third of three species with a body length less than 
<quantity box="[889,967,1770,1797]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.7" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" unit="mm" value="37.0">37 mm</quantity>
and wingspan greater than 
<quantity box="[1272,1366,1770,1797]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.1" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" unit="mm" value="110.0">110 mm</quantity>
. Body length is about 
<quantity box="[329,412,1806,1833]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" unit="mm" value="35.0">35 mm</quantity>
, wingspan about 
<quantity box="[613,763,1806,1833]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.185" metricValueMax="1.2" metricValueMin="1.17" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" unit="mm" value="118.5" valueMax="120.0" valueMin="117.0">117–120 mm</quantity>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Amyot, C. J. B. &amp; Audinet-Serville, A." box="[780,1152,1806,1832]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" refId="ref66726" refString="Amyot, C. J. B. &amp; Audinet-Serville, A. (1843) Histoire Naturelle des Insectes. Hemipteres. Deuxime partie. Homopteres. Homoptera Latr. Librairie encyclopedique de Roret, Paris, 675 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8471" type="book" year="1843">Amyot &amp; Audinet-Serville 1843</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Karsch, F. A. F." box="[1166,1314,1806,1832]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="85 - 130" refId="ref69057" refString="Karsch, F. A. F. (1890) Beitrage zur kenntniss der singcikaden Afrika's und Madagascar's. Berliner Entomologischer Zeitschrift, 35, 85 - 130. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnd. 18900350107" type="journal article" year="1890">Karsch 1890</bibRefCitation>
). It can be distinguished further from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1881" box="[456,546,1843,1868]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Platypleura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gigas">
<emphasis box="[456,546,1843,1868]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">P. gigas</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Karsch" authorityYear="1890" box="[603,689,1842,1868]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Platypleura" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rudis">
<emphasis box="[603,689,1842,1868]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">P. rudis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the piceous spot on the posterior of the lateral sigillae and the ground color cruciform elevation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,1770,1976]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Distribution.—The species is only known from 
<collectingCountry box="[750,885,1914,1940]" name="Madagascar" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Metcalf, Z. P." box="[903,1073,1914,1940]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="1 - 585" refId="ref69829" refString="Metcalf, Z. P. (1963 a) General catalogue of the Homoptera, Fascicle VIII. Cicadoidea. Part 1. Cicadidae. Section I. Tibiceninae. North Carolina State College Contribution, 1502, i-vii + 1 - 585." type="journal article" year="1963">Metcalf 1963a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Duffels, J. P. &amp; van der Laan, P. A." box="[1087,1431,1914,1941]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" refId="ref68709" refString="Duffels, J. P. &amp; van der Laan, P. A. (1985) Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Homoptera, Auchenorhyncha) 1956 - 1980. Series Entomologica 34. Dr. W. Junk Publishers, Dordrect, 414 pp." type="book" year="1985">Duffels &amp; van der Laan 1985</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Sanborn, A. F." box="[151,311,1950,1976]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" refId="ref70566" refString="Sanborn, A. F. (2013) Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Hemiptera: Cicadoidea). With contributions to the bibliography by Martin H. Villet. Elsevier / Academic Press, San Diego, 1001 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / b 978 - 0 - 12 - 416647 - 9.00001 - 2" type="book" year="2013">Sanborn 2013</bibRefCitation>
; 2020).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="17.[151,911,151,178]" box="[151,911,151,178]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,753,151,178]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
Tribe 
<taxonomicName authority="Moulds, 2018" authorityName="Marshall &amp; Moulds" authorityYear="2018" box="[226,590,151,178]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Macrotristriini">Macrotristriini Moulds, 2018</taxonomicName>
(in 
<bibRefCitation author="Marshall, D. C. &amp; Moulds, M. S. &amp; Hill, K. B. R. &amp; Price, B. W. &amp; Wade, E. J. &amp; Owen, C. J. &amp; Goemans, G. &amp; Marathe, K. &amp; Sarkar, V. &amp; Cooley, J. R. &amp; Sanborn, A. F. &amp; Kunte, K. &amp; Villet, M. H. &amp; Simon, C." box="[639,753,152,178]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" pagination="1 - 64" refId="ref69587" refString="Marshall, D. C., Moulds, M. S., Hill, K. B. R., Price, B. W., Wade, E. J., Owen, C. J., Goemans, G., Marathe, K., Sarkar, V., Cooley, J. R., Sanborn, A. F., Kunte, K., Villet, M. H. &amp; Simon, C. (2018 b) A molecular phylogeny of the cicadas (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) with a review of tribe and subfamily level classification. Zootaxa, 4424 (1), 1 - 64. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4424.1.1" type="journal article" year="2018">Marshall</bibRefCitation>
</emphasis>
<emphasis box="[760,812,152,178]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">et al</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[826,911,151,177]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">2018b)</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
